; NAME:
;   AYCAMP_MAKE_WAVE()
;
; PURPOSE:
;   Calculate a wavelength vector of a one-dimensional spectrum
;   using the header parameters.
;
; INPUTS:
;   header - FITS header
;
; OUTPUTS:
;   wave - output wavelength vector
;
; OPTIONAL OUTPUTS:
;   cd1_1  - dispersion [Angstrom/pixel]
;   crval1 - starting wavelength [Angstrom]
;
; PROCEDURES USED:
;   SXPAR()
;
